      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>soft cheese </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>to the pan</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for a further 2 min or until thickened</p>",
      "order": 5,
